00:04:00.900 --> 00:04:03.840
So what makes these cells so attractive for cancer immunotherapy?

71
00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:07.850
Well, the first here is, like any engineered immune cells,

72
00:04:07.920 --> 00:04:09.380
