73
00:04:10.380 --> 00:04:14.060
If someone's repertoire doesn't have the ability to

74
00:04:14.080 --> 00:04:17.800
engage a particular antigen, well, when it's engineered, you've just bypassed

75
00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:21.800
