76
00:04:21.840 --> 00:04:24.820
for CARs. But then they are not HLA restricted,

77
00:04:25.640 --> 00:04:27.490
which means that they can see the

78
00:04:27.780 --> 00:04:31.720
same antigen irrespective of the

79
00:04:32.320 --> 00:04:33.360
restricting HLA.

80
00:04:34.250 --> 00:04:37.610
And that means that they can be used in any patient without

81
00:04:37.640 --> 00:04:41.140
having to pay attention to their

82
