83
00:04:43.420 --> 00:04:46.000
CARs allow for multi-targeted T cells.

84
00:04:47.200 --> 00:04:50.800
Again, the clonotypic physiological receptor is one TCR per

85
00:04:50.900 --> 00:04:51.200
cell.

86
00:04:52.220 --> 00:04:54.040
But in the world of synthetic biology,

87
00:04:56.060 --> 00:04:58.900
researchers are now designing multi-targeted T cells.

88
00:04:59.860 --> 00:05:03.719
Importantly, the CAR, in contrast to the T cell receptor, is not just a targeting

89
00:05:03.780 --> 00:05:07.660
device. It really reprograms functions and metabolism, and that's

90
00:05:07.700 --> 00:05:09.920
through its costimulatory component.

